It took me a week, but I finally finished the garage handrail. While waiting for one piece to be welded by <a href="http://www.ballardsheetmetal.com/">Ballard Sheet Metal</a>, I finished the last bit of perforated aluminum sheeting on the walls and added some trim in the corners to finish it off.

